<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Password Changed Successfully - Homeland Booking</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6; color: #333; background-color: #f4f4f4; margin: 0;
      padding: 20px; } .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: white; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 0 0 20px
      rgba(0,0,0,0.1); overflow: hidden; } .header { background:
      linear-gradient(135deg, #28a745 0%, #20c997 100%); color: white; padding:
      40px 20px; text-align: center; } .header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 300; } .header .icon { font-size: 48px; margin-bottom: 10px;
      } .content { padding: 40px 30px; } .content h2 { color: #28a745;
      margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 24px; } .success-box { background-color:
      #d4edda; border: 1px solid #c3e6cb; border-left: 4px solid #28a745;
      padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 5px; } .info-box {
      background-color: #f8f9ff; border-left: 4px solid #667eea; padding: 20px;
      margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 5px; } .warning-box { background-color:
      #fff3cd; border: 1px solid #ffeaa7; border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
      padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 5px; } .security-tips {
      background-color: #e2e3e5; padding: 20px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px
      0; } .footer { background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 30px; text-align:
      center; color: #666; border-top: 1px solid #eee; } .footer a { color:
      #28a745; text-decoration: none; } .btn { display: inline-block;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #28a745 0%, #20c997 100%); color:
      white; padding: 12px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 50px;
      font-weight: 600; text-align: center; margin: 10px 5px; box-shadow: 0 4px
      15px rgba(40, 167, 69, 0.3); } .btn-secondary { background:
      linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); box-shadow: 0 4px 15px
      rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.3); } .btn-container { text-align: center; margin:
      30px 0; } @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) { .container { margin:
      0; border-radius: 0; } .content { padding: 20px 15px; } .header { padding:
      30px 15px; } }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <div class="icon">‚úÖ</div>
        <h1>Password Changed Successfully</h1>
        <p>Your password has been updated securely</p>
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <h2>Hello {{userName}}!</h2>

        <div class="success-box">
          <p><strong>üéâ Great news!</strong>
            Your password for your Homeland Booking account has been
            successfully changed.</p>
        </div>

        <p>This email confirms that the password for your account
          <strong>{{userEmail}}</strong>
          was changed on
          <strong>{{changeTime}}</strong>.</p>

        <div class="info-box">
          <p><strong>üìç Change Details:</strong></p>
          <ul>
            <li>Date & Time: {{changeTime}}</li>
            <li>IP Address: {{ipAddress}}</li>
            <li>Device: {{userAgent}}</li>
            <li>Location: {{location}}</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="warning-box">
          <p><strong>üö® Didn't make this change?</strong></p>
          <p>If you didn't change your password, your account may be
            compromised. Please take these steps immediately:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Contact our support team right away</li>
            <li>Review your recent account activity</li>
            <li>Check for any unauthorized bookings or changes</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="btn-container">
          <a href="{{loginUrl}}" class="btn">Log In to Your Account</a>
          <a
            href="mailto:support@homelandbooking.com?subject=Unauthorized Password Change"
            class="btn btn-secondary"
          >Report Security Issue</a>
        </div>

        <div class="security-tips">
          <p><strong>üõ°Ô∏è Security Tips:</strong></p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Use a strong password:</strong>
              Combine letters, numbers, and symbols</li>
            <li><strong>Keep it unique:</strong>
              Don't use the same password for other accounts</li>
            <li><strong>Stay vigilant:</strong>
              We'll never ask for your password via email</li>
            <li><strong>Enable notifications:</strong>
              Keep email notifications enabled for security alerts</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <p>Your account security is our top priority. If you have any questions
          or concerns, don't hesitate to reach out to our support team.</p>

        <p>Thank you for keeping your Homeland Booking account secure!</p>

        <p>Best regards,<br />
          <strong>The Homeland Booking Security Team</strong></p>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>This security notification was sent to {{userEmail}}</p>
        <p>¬© 2024 Homeland Booking. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>
          <a href="{{websiteUrl}}">Visit Website</a>
          |
          <a href="mailto:support@homelandbooking.com">Contact Support</a>
          |
          <a href="{{securityCenterUrl}}">Security Center</a>
          |
          <a href="{{privacyPolicyUrl}}">Privacy Policy</a>
        </p>
        <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #999; margin-top: 20px;">
          This is an automated security notification. Please do not reply to
          this email.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>